  title: Why use the new Input System instead of the old Input Manager?
  text: "The new Input System is more powerful, it supports multiple input devices,
    input remapping, and even complex bindings. It\u2019s more scalable for big or
    cross-platform games. The old legacy Input Manager is simpler and great for quick
